page.title: 16SWIMMING
page.content: Most people like to swim. Some like to swim in rivers but most like to swim in a swimming pool like me. My name is Paul Fryer and my hobby is swimming but I don't swim just for pleasure. I like to swim for other people. I'm in the Andover Swimming Club and I go training every Monday, Tuesday and Thursday. I go at half past eight every night. I've been in the Andover swimming squad for just under a year now and I have been in 25 galas since then. My most successful gala was at a town called Guildford when Andover beat l6 other towns and we won the first division shield. My second most successful was when we were against France and we won by 258 to 225. We won a gold cup. Sometimes I go to diving club at l0 o'clock till ll o'clock and that is every Friday. I love swimming.
